In addition, it manufactures and distributes electricity from solar energy; distributes prefab steel and construction materials, as well as solar panels and inverters, including solar system installment; provides tool rental machinery and equipment for electricity, and engineering services and construction work on solar energy; acts as a real estate agents and brokers; manages real estate; and trades in non-residential real estate property. The company was formerly known as Krungthep Keha Group Co., Ltd. Sena Development Public Company Limited was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.

SIRI-R.BK.summary: Sansiri Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the property development business in Thailand. It operates through Property Development; Building Management, Project Management and Real Estate Brokerage; Hotel Management; and Other segments. The Property Development segment develops land and housing projects, as well as residential condominium projects; and rents serviced apartments and office buildings. The Building Management, Project Management and Real Estate Brokerage segment provides building management, property project management, and real estate brokerage services. The Hotel Management segment manages hotels. The Other segment is involved in the hotel and education businesses. The company also offers events management, restaurant club management, and administrative services, as well as distributes standard branded products. The company operates in three segments: Hotel Business; Rental and Management Business; and Real Estate for Sale Business. It develops, rents, and sells real estate properties; leases land and structures; invests in securities; and manages and operates golf course and sports club, as well as manages and operates hotels; owns property; and engages in the office rental business. The company was formerly known as Natural Park Public Company Limited and changed its name to U City Public Company Limited in April 2015. U City Public Company Limited was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.

UNZ.SG.summary: Univentures Public Company Limited engages in the property development business in Thailand. It develops and sells condominiums, as well as rents office buildings. The company also manufactures and sells zinc oxide and chemicals; and provides time recorders, parking control equipment, and electronics equipment. In addition, it offers finance and investment consulting services; investment and management consulting; and other related services. Further, the company operates as a manager of trusts for real estate investments; and invests in energy services, hotel, and other companies. Additionally, it acts as a broker and agent in real estate-related business; and offers corporate registration services. The company was founded in 1980 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand. Univentures Public Company Limited is a subsidiary of Adelfos Company Limited.
